        "management": "Primary prophylaxis with G-CSF (filgrastim 5mcg/kg/day or pegfilgrastim 6mg single dose) if febrile neutropenia risk >20%. Hold if ANC <1000 on day of treatment. Antibiotic prophylaxis if high risk. Transfusion support if Hb <7 or platelets <10."
