        "management": "Triple antiemetic: NK1 RA (aprepitant 125mg day1, 80mg day2-3) + 5-HT3 RA (palonosetron 0.25mg) + dexamethasone 12mg day1, 8mg days 2-4. For cisplatin, continue day 5-8. Consider olanzapine 5-10mg for breakthrough."
