          { "feature": "closed_system_transfer_device_required", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Administer via central line. If extravasation: stop infusion immediately, aspirate residual, apply cold (anthracyclines) or warm (vinca) compresses. Dexrazoxane 1000mg/m2 days 1-2, 500mg/m2 day 3 for anthracycline extravasation. Hyaluronidase for vinca alkaloids. Surgical consult if tissue necrosis."
      },
      {
        "id": "renal_adjusted_dosing",
