          { "feature": "bleomycin_risk_of_pulmonary_toxicity_if_crcl_low", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Carboplatin dose = target AUC x (CrCl + 25). Cisplatin avoid if CrCl <60; split doses if borderline. Methotrexate: hold if CrCl <50, leucovorin rescue based on levels. Bleomycin: reduce dose if CrCl <50. Monitor CrCl before each cycle."
